## 2019-06-10, version 1.0.0 (Current)

### Notable Changes
* Feature [#4](https://github.com/opendistro-for-elasticsearch/job-scheduler/issues/4) Add Support for Elasticsearch 7.0
* Feature [#7](https://github.com/opendistro-for-elasticsearch/job-scheduler/issues/7) Singleton job execution using locking

## 2019-04-10

### Notable Changes

Initial release of JobScheduler plugin. Supports 2 type of schedules
* [Unix Cron](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cron) 
* Interval, defined by
  * start time
  * interval value
  * interval unit

